videos.description: Early in the fourth quarter, Oklahoma State lined up for a field goal to make the de facto Big 12 championship a one-score game. Two plays later, Oklahoma's Joe Mixon was in the end zone. Mike Gundy and Bob Stoops relive the critical turn of events.
videos.headline: Momentum-shifting sequence seals Bedlam for Oklahoma
